It is the 20th in the cycle of combinations. The preceding sign is {{ill|Yang Water Horse|ja|壬午|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, and the following sign is {{ill|Jia Shen|ja|甲申|1=Yang Wood Monkey|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. According to the [[Yin-yang and the Five Elements theory|Yin-Yang and Five Elements theory]], the [[Ten Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stem]] 癸 represents Yin Water, while the [[Earthly Branches|Earthly Branch]] 未 represents Yin Earth, forming a relationship of [[Five Elements#Controlling cycle|mutual restraint]] (Earth restrains Water).
== Years of 癸未 == Years in which the remainder when divided by 60 is 23 correspond to 癸未 in the [[Gregorian calendar]].
